<bibRefCitation id="BB0EFDB7BD28E54C2071D294D2B8F2FE" author="Rumrich, U" journalOrPublisher="Iconographia Diatomologica" pageId="0" pageNumber="23" pagination="1 - 649" refId="B103" refString="Rumrich, U, Lange-Bertalot, H, Rumrich, M, 2000. Diatoms of the Andes. From Venezuela to Patagonia/Tierra del Fuego. Iconographia Diatomologica 9: 1 - 649" title="Diatoms of the Andes. From Venezuela to Patagonia / Tierra del Fuego." volume="9" year="2000">Rumrich et al. 2000</bibRefCitation>
, Diatoms of the Andes from Venezuela to Patagonia/Tierra Del Fuego, Iconographia Diatomologica 9, p. 223-224, Plate 10, Figs 1-11.
